Package ohos.event.notification

Class NotificationConstant

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.event.notification.NotificationConstant

  • public final class NotificationConstant
extends Object
    Provides static constants to indicate notification deletion reasons.

    The constants are the int parameters used when NotificationSubscriber#onCanceled(NotificationRequest, NotificationSortingMap, int) is called.

    Since:
    2
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Notification#ANS
